# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and the working tree.
# Prevents CRLF/LF churn on Windows (core.autocrlf) and keeps Prettier happy.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark known binaries so Git never tries to normalize them.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
